Plot: When George and Timmy go missing, Julian, Dick and Anne are frantic -- what can have happened to them? Then somebody breaks into Kirrin Cottage -- there must be a connection! The Famous Five are ready to solve the mystery, but can they do it without George and Timmy? Cover illustration: Richard Jones
Characters: Jo, George Kirrin (Famous Five), Dick Kirrin, Timmy, Tinker, Anne (Famous Five), Julian (Famous Five), Julian, Dick, Anne, George, Timmy
